                // If N/2 is odd (e.g., N=6, N/2=3):
                //   Chanek takes N/2. Chanek gets 3. N becomes 3.
                //   Opponent must take 1. Opponent gets 1. N becomes 2.
                //   Chanek takes 1. Chanek gets 1. N becomes 1.
